{
  "description": "Golden prompt benchmark for the CAD family registry + prompt classifier. Each case pins the offline classification (family, design mode, generation strategy) and the honesty contract (whether geometry can be generated now, whether export is allowed, and whether clarification/decomposition is expected). These are asserted deterministically with no LLM/CadQuery calls. 'measured_checks' are aspirational ground-truth checks for the cases we also build end-to-end elsewhere.",
